summary: An artist wandering around Whiterun that will carve a sculpture near the front gate.
descriptionHtml:
An artist wandering around Whiterun that will carve a sculpture near the front gate. Not a big mod, hope you enjoy!

~You will know her by the pickaxe on her belt~

*Ingrid is voiced by my wife =)

I posted the following in the attached discussion:
\"So, I\'ve looked into it, and I haven\'t found a way (yet) to duplicate the player\'s model. In the mean time, I am working to add more sculptures for Ingrid to carve! The other options will unlock once you\'ve completed a large side-quest (i.e. become Arch-mage, join the Nightengales, become Harbinger of the Companions)

I don\'t have an ETA, but just thought I should let everyone know what\'s up!\"
author: iscrybble
